  ,
  t3."id" AS "t3_id",
  t3."name" AS "t3_name"

FROM t0
  LEFT JOIN "productTagsTagProductsLinks" t1 ON t1."product_id" = t0."id"
  LEFT JOIN "tags" t2 ON t2."id" = t1."tag_id"
